// Title: New Domain Contacted by Endpoint
// Description: Identifies endpoints communicating with domains not commonly seen in the environment
// Data Source: DeviceNetworkEvents
// MITRE ATT&CK:
//   Tactic: TA0001 - Initial Access
//   Technique: T1189 - Drive-by Compromise
// Severity: Medium

DeviceNetworkEvents
| where isnotempty(RemoteUrl)
| summarize ConnectionCount = count()
    by DeviceName, RemoteUrl
| where ConnectionCount <= 3
| project DeviceName, RemoteUrl